Description: Egypt, view of pigeon house with ornate clay roof. Set amongst palm trees [oasis?]. Medium: Gelatin silver print.
Producer name: Photographed by: John Frederick Clifford Hunt
Curator's comments: People may also live in such "pigeon houses". J M Hudson, 29/01/1998. Geography: Kurna not identified in sources. Location and alternative spellings suggested by J M Hudson, 29/01/1997. Circumstances: The Imperial War Museum holds photographs from the same collection with a more military content - see [HUN-] PIC DOC 66.
